song_lyrics: Sakhī din upar din jāye, dhīraj kem dharie... 1
Sakhī pīyu viyoge paḷ, jāye jug jevaḍī;
Sakhī dāzīne uṭhe chhe dal, ghaṇu ghaḍī ghaḍī... 2
Sakhī faḍakī ūṭhu paḍe fāḷ, pīyu pardeshaḍe;
Sakhī antare ūṭhe chhe zāḷ, sukh nahī sandeshaḍe... 3
Sakhī evaḍalu am sāth, karīne kem gayā;
Sakhī Niṣhkuḷānandno Nāth, hajī kem nā’viyā... 4
title: Sakhī Chaitare chintā thāy kaho kem karīe
